
Dear U2 Fan,

U2's exclusive session for BBC Radio One, of new material from All That You
Can't Leave Behind, is to be broadcast live on U2.com on Monday 23rd
October.

The band will be interviewed and will perform a live set during the Simon
Mayo and Jo Whiley shows which will take place at the BBC's Maida Vale
Studios, London.  The session starts at 11am until 1pm (GMT).

The full interview and all songs performed will be web-cast live on
http://www.U2.com


Best wishes
u2.com


